---
// Toronto Subsidy Information Component
---

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cyan-200">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
        City of Toronto Basement Flooding Protection Subsidy
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-cyan-700 font-semibold">
        Get Up to $3,400 in Subsidies - We Handle Everything!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
          <div class="bg-cyan-50 rounded-full p-3 mr-3">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Backwater Valve</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-600 mb-2">Up to $1,250</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 80% of installation cost covered</li>
          <li>• Maximum $1,250 subsidy</li>
          <li>• Permit included</li>
          <li>• Prevents sewage backup</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
          <div class="bg-cyan-50 rounded-full p-3 mr-3">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Sump Pump</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-600 mb-2">Up to $1,750</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 80% of installation cost covered</li>
          <li>• Maximum $1,750 subsidy</li>
          <li>• Battery backup eligible</li>
          <li>• 24/7 flood protection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
          <div class="bg-purple-100 rounded-full p-3 mr-3">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Drain Severance</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">Up to $400</p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
          <li>• 80% of severance cost covered</li>
          <li>• Maximum $400 subsidy</li>
          <li>• Disconnects storm drains</li>
          <li>• Reduces system overload</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">How Dryspace Handles Your Subsidy</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-100 rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Free Assessment</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">We evaluate your eligibility and maximize your subsidy</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-100 rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Permit Filing</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">We handle all permit applications and approvals</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-100 rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Installation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Professional installation meeting all City requirements</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-orange-100 rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-2">
            <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Subsidy Claim</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">We submit all paperwork and ensure you get maximum refund</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Important Requirements</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Property must be in City of Toronto</li>
            <li>• Work must be done by licensed contractor (that's us!)</li>
            <li>• Permits must be obtained before work begins</li>
            <li>• City inspection required for subsidy approval</li>
            <li>• Subsidy applies to labor and materials only</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">
        Don't leave money on the table! Let Dryspace maximize your subsidy.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/toronto-subsidy" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-cyan-700 transition-colors">
          Learn More About Subsidies
        </a>
        <a href="/free-inspection" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-orange-700 transition-colors">
          Check Your Eligibility - Free
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>